{"tid":1590781,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"田北辰賣港，要求荃灣起智慧燈柱","createTime":"2019-09-24T01:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T09:17:18.000Z","uid":170634,"like":47,"dislike":395,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"c0bf031bbf70a57a2c06ff7e0462fd10a3549a8c","tid":1590781,"uid":170634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLJXGUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLJXGUF.jpg&h=fc29fed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/tw/doc/2016_2019/tc/committee_meetings_minutes/TTC/TTC_17_Minutes_1819c.pdf?fbclid=IwAR1A9VilEXW5BB7QA50_HLITuExzWkMDgsGSmYv_WZPxs1ROEvl9Q2bStNI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Ftw%2Fdoc%2F2016_2019%2Ftc%2Fcommittee_meetings_minutes%2FTTC%2FTTC_17_Minutes_1819c.pdf%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1A9VilEXW5BB7QA50_HLITuExzWkMDgsGSmYv_WZPxs1ROEvl9Q2bStNI&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=113bb405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/tw/doc/2016_2019/tc/committee_meetings_minutes/TTC/TTC_17_Minutes_1819c.pdf?fbclid=IwAR1A9VilEXW5BB7QA50_HLITuExzWkMDgsGSmYv_WZPxs1ROEvl9Q2bStNI</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;XII 第 11 項議程：要求荃灣區試行引入多功能智慧燈柱<br />\n（交通第 40/18-19 號文件）<br />\n72. 主席表示，田北辰議員、鄭㨗彬議員、馬庭熙先生及范煦瑜女士提交有關文<br />\n件，並介紹出席是次會議的政府資訊科技總監辦公室總系統經理（智慧城市）湯<br />\n文光先生及路政署高級工程師／1 鄭重山先生。<br />\n<br />\n政府資訊科技總監辦公室總系統經理（智慧城市）回應，政府於二零一七年<br />\n的《施政報告》中提及會試行多功能智慧燈柱，並計劃於未來三年分階段更換或<br />\n安裝 400 支智慧燈柱，其中大約 50 支會在二零一九年六月前在觀塘及啟德區內<br />\n安裝，其餘的燈柱將由二零二零年起陸續於中環／金鐘、銅鑼灣／灣仔及尖沙咀<br />\n安裝，現時已展開前期準備工程。該辦公室會在試行安裝首 50 支智慧燈柱後檢<br />\n視成果，再考慮會否把荃灣納入試行計劃中。另外，政府即將安裝的智慧燈柱已<br />\n包括大部分的建議功能，委員亦可按計劃成果提出新的功能以供考慮。<br />\n<br />\n75. 委員的意見及提問摘錄如下：<br />\n(1) 詢問第二批 350 支智慧燈柱的安裝時間表（主席）；以及<br />\n(2) 認為荃灣區內的新樓盤將陸續落成，對有關設備需求殷切，希望可把荃<br />\n灣納入安裝第二批 350 支智慧燈柱試驗計劃，並把有關計劃擴展至全港<br />\n各區（副主席）。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n田北辰議員、鄭㨗彬議員出賣香港,一定要踢走建制派!"},{"pid":"77b640dda500d3bf33b45b82076388008283add4","tid":1590781,"uid":170634,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:37:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=483465302203788&amp;id=444619249421727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D483465302203788%26id%3D444619249421727&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=1405f9d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=483465302203788&amp;id=444619249421727</a>"},{"pid":"d862ed73e0d840e43112c10a0dc385ce544799ba","tid":1590781,"uid":19218,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:42:50.000Z","msg":"癲"},{"pid":"325b65e5a61ecd190ea8921856ac45815142e041","tid":1590781,"uid":244034,"like":112,"dislike":1,"score":111,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:44:23.000Z","msg":"條本身就牆頭草邊邊有利就企果度"},{"pid":"fb8c1a1e16c24fd4d2d817957342aa4980730037","tid":1590781,"uid":244034,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友本身就牆頭草邊邊有利就企果度</blockquote>"},{"pid":"76be7eafe3ad89a4f2858db652d0edf6a627294e","tid":1590781,"uid":80777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:45:41.000Z","msg":"推俾更多人睇"},{"pid":"a9a09076b22d9a6a0131ba7271f102548715c30d","tid":1590781,"uid":170634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:46:06.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n831"},{"pid":"6d1e293f64f57a539e5e1048e8d2a491f0d3a89c","tid":1590781,"uid":55130,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:46:46.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n一向都賣港"},{"pid":"9ba088adae62f315fc132c5940af8d610eb861d4","tid":1590781,"uid":38317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:47:03.000Z","msg":"Pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig