買日2. 教育家中兩老3. 去連儂牆幫手<br />\n每月任務：1. 換美金，走資2. 陪審員/派傳單/放映會/各有各做<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=f950099e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=af3dd184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obkYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=810fa021\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.09.24"},{"pid":"4cd99826859d70668da8876fec175b3e5fe671cf","tid":1590781,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a66464bb63f5e9d339cbd40729137e583a37a73","tid":1590781,"uid":194968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:28:27.000Z","msg":"狗改不了吃屎"},{"pid":"f91d11aac3d6388d805a66801513b3fa8441f313","tid":1590781,"uid":55028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:29:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eb3f3f6a652e67a25e878833fe4b220d8673a880","tid":1590781,"uid":293914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦 舊年真係冇人知燈柱會侵犯個人私隱，反而果時見個設計靚過舊款，同識得監測天氣數據都幾期待佢推出，點知集體中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6464a3e2387cf9684b6747c48e24e774801dc7a9","tid":1590781,"uid":170634